snippet.textDisplay: I'm seeing everyone saying this is amazing .. goosebumps etc. idk to me this song .. I don't hate it after 5 listens but I also don't love it.. from the arrangement standpoint it felt too basic ...I like the percussion and the choir , he sung it nicely too .. I liked the dacehall vibe they were going for.. but somehow it didn't make me feel anything ..sooo much could've been done.. I don't want to criticize because I've always been a fan since season 2 but I have to say a lot of songs this season don't deserve the coke studio tag .
